ink><description>两名美国议员将于周四提出立法，大幅扩大政府对来自中国和其他构成国家安全担忧的外国买家购买房地产的外国投资审查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:37:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-lawmakers-propose-legislation-seeking-more-scrutiny-chinese-real-estate-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：意大利与中国奇瑞就汽车工厂进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-with-chinas-chery-car-plant-2024-03-13/</link><description>两名消息人士告诉路透社，意大利政府正在与中国奇瑞汽车进行谈判，以吸引除 Stellantis 之外的另一家主要汽车制造商进入该国并增加国内汽车产量。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:34:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-with-chinas-chery-car-plant-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车表示其ID.UNYX车型已获得中国政府批准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-says-it-has-received-chinese-government-approval-idunyx-model-2024-03-13/</link><description>大众汽车集团（中国）周三表示，其唯一控股的合资企业安徽大众汽车的首款车型已获得中国政府批准。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:11:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-says-it-has-received-chinese-government-approval-idunyx-model-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院通过法案迫使字节跳动剥离 TikTok 或面临禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-house-vote-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-ban-2024-03-13/</link><description>美国众议院周三以压倒性多数通过了一项法案，该法案将给予 TikTok 的中国所有者字节跳动大约六个月的时间剥离这款短视频应用程序的美国资产，否则将面临禁令，这是自特朗普政府以来该应用程序面临的最大威胁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:01:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-house-vote-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-ban-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国煤炭集团表示，美国对俄罗斯的限制是为了保持高价格，损害了出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-coal-group-says-us-curbs-russia-keep-prices-high-hurt-exports-2024-03-13/</link><description>中国一个行业组织周三警告称，美国对俄罗斯煤炭公司更严厉的制裁将在短期内使全球高热值煤炭价格保持在高位，影响俄罗斯五分之一的煤炭出口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 08:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-coal-group-says-us-curbs-russia-keep-prices-high-hurt-exports-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>抵押贷款违约率上升给中国家庭带来更多痛苦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rising-mortgage-defaults-bring-more-pain-chinese-households-2024-03-13/</link><description>在中国南方城市，前金融工作者雷晓宇因抵押贷款拖欠而被收债人追捕，她不再接听电话，试图推迟不可避免的事情。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:06:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rising-mortgage-defaults-bring-more-pain-chinese-households-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>河北省发生特大爆炸，造成2人死亡26人受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/explosion-hebei-china-restaurant-injures-several-people-state-media-reports-2024-03-13/</link><description>官方媒体和当局周三表示，中国北部省份河北省一家餐馆疑似煤气泄漏，引发爆炸，建筑物外墙被撕裂，汽车受损，碎片散落，造成两人死亡、26 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 02:42:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/explosion-hebei-china-restaurant-injures-several-people-state-media-reports-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>股市持平，美国国债收益率在数据公布前小幅走高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-13/</link><description>周三，全球股市指数几乎没有变化，在欧洲和美国股市前一交易日触及创纪录水平后暂停，投资者关注下一轮通胀和消费者健康数据。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 02:16:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪推出新版e2掀背车，起售价更低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launches-new-version-e2-hatchback-with-lower-starting-price-2024-03-13/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪周三推出了新版 e2 EV 掀背车，起价低于其前身。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:39:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launches-new-version-e2-hatchback-with-lower-starting-price-2024-03-13/</guid></item><i